    <item>
      <title>欧洲银行将延长与印度清算公司的交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/european-banks-said-to-extend-dealing-with-indian-clearing-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，由于监管权力之争可能导致交易中断，法国和德国的市场监管机构要求其银行在 10 月底的最后期限之后继续与印度清算所进行交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/european-banks-said-to-extend-dealing-with-indian-clearing-firms</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 08:46:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特金融公司 2.64 亿美元 IPO 几分钟内全部完成</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/saudi-finance-firm-united-international-s-ipo-fully-covered-in-minutes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯金融服务公司联合国际控股有限公司 (United International Holding Co.) 首次公开募股 (IPO) 高达 9.9 亿里亚尔（2.64 亿美元），认购开始几分钟后，所有股票便获得抢购，表明该地区对上市的需求持续存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/saudi-finance-firm-united-international-s-ipo-fully-covered-in-minutes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 08:26:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济低迷 泰国商业团体呼吁出台更多刺激措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/thai-business-groups-press-for-more-stimulus-as-economy-sputters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国主要商业团体和商业银行敦促总理巴东丹·西那瓦推出新措施刺激消费支出，并解决泰国家庭债务水平居亚洲最高之一的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/thai-business-groups-press-for-more-stimulus-as-economy-sputters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 08:18:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>地缘政治担忧缓解，航空股上涨，欧洲股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/european-stocks-gain-as-lack-of-mideast-escalation-gives-a-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市上涨，因为投资者准备迎接又一个繁忙的收益周，并且以色列对伊朗进行有限袭击后地缘政治担忧有所缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/european-stocks-gain-as-lack-of-mideast-escalation-gives-a-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 08:15:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音公司计划最早于周一增资逾 150 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/boeing-plans-over-15-billion-capital-raise-as-soon-as-monday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，波音公司计划最早于周一启动融资，此举将有助于这家陷入困境的飞机制造商提高流动性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/boeing-plans-over-15-billion-capital-raise-as-soon-as-monday</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 23:45:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关键一周伊始，股市上涨，油价下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/yen-drops-as-japan-election-unnerves-investors-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列对伊朗的报复性打击避开了石油设施后，市场弥漫着一种宽慰的感觉，在对投资者来说至关重要的一周开始时，原油价格暴跌，股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/yen-drops-as-japan-election-unnerves-investors-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 22:34:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券市场遭遇抛售，将迎来为期 10 天的考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/a-10-day-test-is-coming-for-bond-market-battered-by-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国债券市场已经遭遇了六个月来最严重的抛售，目前正进入关键的两周，这可能会决定今年剩余时间的走势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/a-10-day-test-is-coming-for-bond-market-battered-by-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 14:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
